This story about a guy who has lost the meaming of life because of his
brides death.Drinking and depression made him get behind the wheel of his
car and commit suicide in the same place and by the same way where she died.
He survived, but fell into a coma, where his soul got into the world of the
dead. Being a prosoner of this place, he keeps a diary where tells us
everything about this world.


1. Unrar.
2. Burn or mount the image.
3. Install the game.
4. Add the eulafix.reg key located in /Crack directory to your Windows
   registry
5. Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack directory on the image to
   your game install directory.
6. Play the game.
7. Support the software developers. If you like this game, BUY IT!
